data.description: Introducing this modern 3BR 2BA home nestled in the highly desirable Zillah Lakes neighborhood. This charming property offers 1300 sq ft of comfortable living space, making it ideal to call home. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a beautifully updated interior featuring newer flooring and showcasing the stunning new granite counter tops and backsplash. The open-concept living and dining area creates a welcoming space for relaxation and entertaining. The kitchen also features modern appliances, ample cabinet space, and a convenient layout, making it a perfect space to host.The home is situated in the sought-after Zillah Lakes, known for it's picturesque surroundings and tranquil atmosphere. Residents of this community enjoy access to a private golf course, walking trails, serene lakeside settings and have access to the beautiful lake for paddle boarding, kayaking or other forms of non-motorized toys.
